T02TD2919E:316a-1: badzra bi d'a ra na karma tsa tu:s'a dha na bi dhi:/
T02TD2919E:316a-3: rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa'i las bzhi sgrub pa'i cho ga / rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2919E:316a-4: gnyis med ye shes rdo rje can //
T02TD2919E:316a-6: 'byung ba bzhi la brten pa'i las //
T02TD2919E:316a-7: tshar gcad rjes su gzung ba bshad //
T02TD2919E:316a-8: sa phyogs gang du gnod pa'i las //
T02TD2919E:316a-9: sgrub par 'os pa der gnas te //
T02TD2919E:316a-10: tshva sgo can nas sa blangs la //
T02TD2919E:316a-11: thab khung me dbyibs nag pos byug / gnag dang 'khyol dang dri nga dang //
T02TD2919E:316a-12: srin gyis rnam par zos pa dang //
T02TD2919E:316a-13: reg nas zug rngu bskyed pa'i shing //
T02TD2919E:316a-14: khung dang rjes mthun dbyibs su brtsig / gu gul nag po n'a ri'i sha //
T02TD2919E:316a-15: khva yi gshog pa bong bu'i spangs //
T02TD2919E:316a-16: mche ba can gyi rtug pa dang //
T02TD2919E:316a-17: yungs kar gdon rnams tshar gcod byed //
T02TD2919E:316a-18: til dang me tog nag po dang //
T02TD2919E:316a-19: ma sha la sogs 'bru nag bcas//
T02TD2919E:316a-20: dug khrag tsha ba'i mar khu rnams //
T02TD2919E:316a-21: skyes pa'i yan lag las byung ba'i //
T02TD2919E:316a-22: snod dam yang na lcags kyi snod //
T02TD2919E:316a-23: nim pa'i shing lo'i snod bzhag nas //
T02TD2919E:316a-24: rdo gnyis gtsubs las byung ba'am //
T02TD2919E:316a-25: rngon pa'i khyim blangs me sbar te //
T02TD2919E:316a-26: de'i dbus ram las drag po'i me //
T02TD2919E:316a-27: khro gzugs 'jigs par byed pa po //
T02TD2919E:316a-28: mdog nag rnam par gtsigs pa'i zhal //
T02TD2919E:316a-29: bgrang phreng mi 'jigs sbyin pa dang //
T02TD2919E:316a-30: dbyu gu rtse gsum spyi blugs 'dzin //
T02TD2919E:316a-32: ra yi gdan la gnas pa bskyed //
T02TD2919E:316a-33: ye shes me ni spyan drangs te //
T02TD2919E:316a-34: de dang gnyis su med byas la //
T02TD2919E:316a-35: mchod dang bstod pas mnyes par byas//
T02TD2919E:316a-39: sarbba karma ma he shva ra sarba dusht'a na m'a ra ya h'um phat /
T02TD2919E:316a-40: sngags bcas rdzas rnams tsha ba yi //
T02TD2919E:316a-41: mar la spags te me la dbul //
T02TD2919E:316a-42: slar yang mchod dang bstod pa yis //
T02TD2919E:316a-43: mnyes par byas la mi dbus su //
T02TD2919E:316a-44: rang lha bskyed dang ye shes gzhug / der yang mchod dang bstod byas te//
T02TD2919E:316b-0: @316b tsha ba'i mar gyis spags pa'i rdzas //
T02TD2919E:316b-1: sngags bcas bsregs pas lha mnyes byas //
T02TD2919E:316b-2: 'dir yang de bzhin mchod pa dang //
T02TD2919E:316b-3: bstod pas mnyes byas sgrub gsol dang //
T02TD2919E:316b-4: yi ge brgya ba'i gsang sngags kyis //
T02TD2919E:316b-5: yongs su dag pas mnyes par bya //
T02TD2919E:316b-6: rdo rje'i sngags kyis lha gshegs te //
T02TD2919E:316b-7: slar yang mi dmigs mchod pa dang //
T02TD2919E:316b-8: bsreg dang mchod dang las sgrub par //
T02TD2919E:316b-9: gsol btab nas ni gshegs gsol bya //
T02TD2919E:316b-10: 'dis ni sgrub la bar gcod pa'i //
T02TD2919E:316b-11: bgegs med dngos grub sbyin par byed //
T02TD2919E:316b-12: dpal rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa'i las su bya ba me dang 'brel ba'o /
T02TD2919E:316b-14: // / thal ba mtshan ngan snod gzhag pa //
T02TD2919E:316b-15: der ni bgegs kyi gzugs bris la //
T02TD2919E:316b-16: dkyil 'khor dur khrod so phag gis //
T02TD2919E:316b-17: me gzugs bris ba'i steng du gzhag / rang lhar bsgoms pa'i snying ga yi //
T02TD2919E:316b-18: ye shes yi ge'i 'od zer gyis //
T02TD2919E:316b-19: bgegs kun mdun gyi sngags la bstim //
T02TD2919E:316b-20: sngags 'od me bzhin tsha ba yis //
T02TD2919E:316b-21: bsreg par bsam zhing bzlas pa'i mthar //
T02TD2919E:316b-22: yungs kar yungs nag ske tshe dug / gsang sngags bzlas dang bcas pas brab //
T02TD2919E:316b-23: skyes pa'i rkang dam seng ldeng gi //
T02TD2919E:316b-24: phur bu sngags bcas snying gar bsnun //
T02TD2919E:316b-25: de mthar gzugs bcas thal ba la //
T02TD2919E:316b-26: rnam par 'thor ba'i sbyor ba yis //
T02TD2919E:316b-27: tshar gcod bgegs med grub sbyin byed //
T02TD2919E:316b-28: dpal rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa'i las su bya ba rlung dang 'brel bas 'thor ba'o //
T02TD2919E:316b-29: bsregs pa'i thal ba tshva sgo can //
T02TD2919E:316b-30: shing gcig rtsa ba 'jug ngogs sa //
T02TD2919E:316b-31: nim pa'i khu bas sbrus pa las //
T02TD2919E:316b-32: bgegs gzugs snying gar sngags bris gzhug / rang lha ye shes yi ge yi //
T02TD2919E:316b-33: 'od kyis bgegs bkug gzugs la bstim //
T02TD2919E:316b-35: bsam gtan ldan pas rig sngags bzlas //
T02TD2919E:316b-37: nga ro 'don pa'i rtags thob nas //
T02TD2919E:316b-38: mchod rten mtshan ma gcig pa la //
T02TD2919E:316b-39: dur khrod ma mo'i khyim du sba //
T02TD2919E:316b-40: sbyor 'dis sgrub la bar gcod pa //
T02TD2919E:316b-41: bcings nas bgegs med dngos grub ster //
T02TD2919E:316b-42: dpal rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa'i las su bya ba sa dang 'brel pa mnan pa'o /
T02TD2919E:316b-44: // / dben par tshva sgo can sa la //
T02TD2919E:316b-45: dug dang khrag sbyar chus spags pas //
T02TD2919E:316b-46: dkyil 'khor gru gsum dug dang khrag / ro bsregs sol bas nag por byug /
T02TD2919E:317a-0: @317a * // der ni bum pa kha dog gnag / sngon po'i ras kyis ma kul dgris te //
T02TD2919E:317a-1: gdug pa'i shing gis kha brgyan ngas //
T02TD2919E:317a-2: rgyun bral chu yis legs bkang ste //
T02TD2919E:317a-3: der yang ming rus yungs kar dang //
T02TD2919E:317a-4: dug khrag gu gul ske tshe gzhug / rang lha'i rnal 'byor ldan pa yis //
T02TD2919E:317a-5: bum nang yam ram bam bhr'um las//
T02TD2919E:317a-6: rlung gnas me steng chu dkyil 'khor //
T02TD2919E:317a-7: bsgoms te rang snying sa bon las //
T02TD2919E:317a-8: bgegs bkug 'khor lo'i lte bar gzhug / sngags kyi 'od kyis bskul ba'i rlung //
T02TD2919E:317a-9: rnam par g-yos pas me spar te //
T02TD2919E:317a-10: rab tu khol ba'i chu rlabs dang //
T02TD2919E:317a-11: bsregs pa'i 'khor los bgegs kyi lus //
T02TD2919E:317a-12: nyam thag byed bsgom gsang sngags bzlas //
T02TD2919E:317a-13: sbyor ba 'di yis ji srid du //
T02TD2919E:317a-14: mngon par 'dod pa rdzogs pa dang //
T02TD2919E:317a-15: gang gi lus la chus reg pa //
T02TD2919E:317a-16: bgegs kyi gnod pa las grol 'gyur //
T02TD2919E:317a-17: dpal rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa'i las su bya ba chu dang 'brel pas bkru ba'o //
T02TD2919E:317a-18: rdo rje can gyi las gang gis //
T02TD2919E:317a-19: ma rungs gdon bgegs tshar bcad nas //
T02TD2919E:317a-22: rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa'i las bzhi sgrub pa'i cho ga / bram ze ma ni badzras mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2919E:317a-24: // / pandi ta chen po dzny'a na shr'i dang /
T02TD2919E:317a-25: lo ts'a ba ra ba zhi bshes gnyen gyis bsgyur ba'o//
